        "content": "<p>Thinking about how to finish off the last few sorries for 8.19, it seems we will need the following: If <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span></span></span></span> is a profinite set which happens to be a <em>cofiletered</em> limit <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\"><munder accentunder=\"true\"><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">l</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">i</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi></mrow><mo stretchy=\"true\">←</mo></munder></mi><mo>⁡</mo></mrow><mi>i</mi></msub><msub><mi>X</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">X = \\varprojlim_i X_i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.26614em;vertical-align:-0.5717em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\"><span class=\"mop\"><span class=\"mord accentunder\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.69444em;\"><span class=\"svg-align\" style=\"top:-2.4779999999999998em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><sp